data.description: Luxury meets comfort in this magnificent custom pool home! Offering 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, this residence boasts 2800sq feet of living space bathed in natural light. The soaring architectural double tray ceilings add a touch of grandeur, while the expansive chef's quality kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream. With a 3-car garage, large closets, generous room sizes, this home is the epitome of refined living. The roof was replace in 2022, water heater 2023, and the HVAC in 2018, new screen replacement 2023, new inside paint 2023. Other great features include: salt water heated pool with jacuzzi, whole house surround sound, pool bath, oversized corner lot and a huge outdoor kitchen/living area. Square footage received from tax rolls. All information recorded in the MLS intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
